p://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  Roleplaying </span><hr size=1> Elhimac made a post in the Mods section that he is thinking about leaving MMDN. He is disappointed because his Roleplaying section isn't seeing much action. I am not much of a roleplayer. But I do feel that he provides a valuable service for those who do. I for one would hate to see him go. I hope he reconsiders. I am posting this here so that maybe others will post here asking him to stay also. He seems like a great guy and tries to do many things to make EQ fun for so many people. <br>
